sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh<br/>(external pod)
    participant Puller as model-serving-puller<br/>8084/TCP gRPC
    participant Adapter as runtime-adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(Triton/OVMS/MLServer/TorchServe)
    participant Storage as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Secret as /storage-config<br/>Mounted Secret

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over MM,Storage: Flow 1: Model Loading (Puller + Adapter)
        MM->>Puller: LoadModel(modelId, modelType, modelPath, modelKey)<br/>gRPC :8084 plaintext
        Puller->>Secret: Read storage credentials<br/>filesystem mount
        Secret-->>Puller: S3/GCS/Azure/HTTP credentials
        Puller->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS :443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Cloud provider auth
        Storage-->>Puller: Model files → /models/_ovms_models/{id}
        Puller->>Adapter: LoadModel(modelId, modelType, modelPath)<br/>gRPC :8085 plaintext
        Adapter->>Runtime: Runtime-specific load<br/>gRPC :8001 or HTTP :8001 or gRPC :7071
        Runtime-->>Adapter: Load result (success/failure)
        Adapter-->>Puller: LoadModel response (sizeInBytes, maxConcurrency)
        Puller-->>MM: LoadModel response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over MM,Storage: Flow 2: Model Loading (Embedded Puller)
        MM->>Adapter: LoadModel(modelId, modelType, modelPath, modelKey)<br/>gRPC :8085 plaintext
        Adapter->>Secret: Read storage credentials<br/>filesystem mount
        Secret-->>Adapter: S3/GCS/Azure/HTTP credentials
        Adapter->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS :443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Cloud provider auth
        Storage-->>Adapter: Model files → /models/_ovms_models/{id}
        Adapter->>Runtime: Runtime-specific load<br/>gRPC :8001 or HTTP :8001 or gRPC :7071
        Runtime-->>Adapter: Load result
        Adapter-->>MM: LoadModel response (sizeInBytes, maxConcurrency)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 3: Runtime Status Check
        MM->>Adapter: RuntimeStatus()<br/>gRPC :8085 plaintext
        Adapter->>Runtime: Health check<br/>ServerReady / Ping / GET /v1/config
        Runtime-->>Adapter: Status (READY/NOT_READY)
        Adapter-->>MM: RuntimeStatusResponse<br/>(status, capacityInBytes, defaultModelSize,<br/>maxLoadingConcurrency, modelLoadingTimeoutMs)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 4: Model Unloading
        MM->>Puller: UnloadModel(modelId)<br/>gRPC :8084 plaintext
        Puller->>Adapter: UnloadModel(modelId)<br/>gRPC :8085 plaintext
        Adapter->>Runtime: Runtime-specific unload<br/>RepositoryModelUnload / UnregisterModel / config reload
        Runtime-->>Adapter: Unload result
        Adapter-->>Puller: UnloadModel response
        Puller-->>MM: UnloadModel response
        Note over Puller: Cleanup: delete model files from /models/
    end
